of the house subcommittee on asian affairs calls blocking a khmer 
rouge return one of the major political and moral challenges of 
the new administration 
the chinese in turn may press washington to increase aid to the 
noncommunist guerrilla groups the forces of prince norodom 
sihanouk and of son sann 
