cambodian factions to engage in dialogue until the next such talks 
can be arranged 
their antagonism in jakarta however has dimmed prospects that 
the cambodians will make progress in talks among themselves three 
rounds of talks between the principal leaders of the two sides 
sihanouk and premier hun sen of the provietnamese government have 
sharpened mutual recriminations 
