teach their children the importance of mourning for the late emperor 
another nationally circulated japanese daily mainichi shimbun 
said 
although the government has asked people to conduct a 
nationwide meditation at noon the decision of whether to express 
mourning should be left up to each individual 
unlike the days of previous deified emperors this funeral 
is the first one under the new constitution it should be a concise 
ceremony suitable for the symbolic emperor 
