boeing confirmed on wednesday that the repeated wiring mishaps 
have prompted the company to start an engineering study in an effort 
to prevent crossed wires and pipes in all boeing models 
there would be changes in the plugs and sockets so that for 
example an individual wire can only go into a particular socket 
boeing spokesman craig martin said 
