and light trucks rose 17 percent from yearearlier levels as the 
effects of sales incentives available in early 1988 began to wear 
off the automakers said thursday 
the eight automakers said they sold cars and light trucks at an 
average daily rate of 36769 during the feb 1120 period this year 
