litton industries inc a maker of 
ships automated factory equipment and electronic gear said its 
profit rose 7 percent in both the three months and the six months 
ended jan 31 
litton said wednesday it earned 435 million or 171 a share 
in the quarter up from 407 million or 156 a share in the 
three months ended jan 31 1988 sales for the most recent quarter 
were 12 billion up from 116 billion a year earlier 
in the six months ended jan 31 profit was 87 million or 340 
a share up from 813 million or 307 a share in the same period 
of last year sales were 243 billion up from 235 billion a year 
earlier 
